Introduction

Park Sun Young, better known by her stage name Luna, is a South Korean singer, actress, and presenter. She is best known as the main vocalist and lead dancer of South Korean girl group f(x). Luna made her solo debut with the extended play Free Somebody on May 31, 2016.

In September 2019, Luna officially left SM Entertainment.
